00:21.830 --> 00:23.580
♪ Running in a blurry hurry ♪

00:26.080 --> 00:27.000
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:28.380 --> 00:30.670
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:30.670 --> 00:32.210
♪ Canines on the run ♪

00:32.210 --> 00:34.080
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:34.080 --> 00:35.540
♪ Them doggone dogs are fun ♪

00:35.540 --> 00:36.960
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:36.960 --> 00:39.580
♪ Without fail you'll wind up
chasing your tail ♪

00:39.580 --> 00:41.580
♪ What's the harm
in revelrous adventures ♪

00:41.580 --> 00:43.500
♪

00:43.500 --> 00:44.710
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:45.960 --> 00:47.170
♪ Life's just a bed of roses ♪

00:47.170 --> 00:48.330
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:48.330 --> 00:50.540
